      "value": "<p>Requirements: Ghoul.</p><p>Your body has seen the worst the wasteland has to offer. If  you ever lose any of your limbs, besides your head, you  can spend 5 minutes reattaching the limb so long as you  have a first aid kit and you still have the limb you lost.  Additionally, you can spend 1 minute to heal a number of  hit points equal to your healing rate. Once you heal in this  way, you cannot do it again until you rest for at least 6  hours</p>",
